CustomField.description: No longer used. Initially was part of setting the 'AJWS Organization ID' for Grantee Account. However, 'AJWS Organization ID' is now = GIFTS ID which is set by automation. This was done to avoid setting 'AJWS Organization ID' for donor Accounts.
